    "body": "Thank you for taking the time to report this issue. We truly appreciate your feedback.\n\nWe are currently experiencing a service outage that may be affecting your experience with GitHub Copilot.\n\n**What you can do:**\n- Please subscribe to #302112 for real-time updates on the service outage\n- Once the service outage is resolved, please give it another try\n- If you continue to experience issues after the outage is resolved, please don't hesitate to file a new issue\n\nWe're closing this issue as a duplicate to help us consolidate the discussion and better track the service outage. Your report helps us understand the impact of the outage, and we apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused.\n\nThank you for your patience and understanding.",
